                        <paragraph>Xylitol, Microcrystalline Cellulose, Povidone, Magnesium Stearate, Talc, Fruit Punch Flavor, Sucralose.</paragraph>
                     </text>
                     <effectiveTime value="20120503"/>
                  </section>
